***dblink 错误
oracle连接DBLINK报错:ORA-12154: TNS:could not resolve service name的解决办法
原因是建dblink的时候 using 后边的 引号里加服务名了
如下边的第一个就是错误的
create database LINK to39act
　　connect to UCR_PARAM6 identified by UCR_PARAM6
　　using '39NGACT = /**错误*/
(DESCRIPTION =
    (ADDRESS = (PROTOCOL = TCP)(HOST = 10.124.0.39)(PORT = 1521))
    (CONNECT_DATA =
      (SERVER = DEDICATED)
      (SERVICE_NAME = ngact)
    )
)';

---正确的
create database LINK to39act
　　connect to UCR_PARAM6 identified by UCR_PARAM6
　　using '(DESCRIPTION =
    (ADDRESS = (PROTOCOL = TCP)(HOST = 10.124.0.39)(PORT = 1521))
    (CONNECT_DATA =
      (SERVER = DEDICATED)
      (SERVICE_NAME = ngact)
    )
)';



